# Personal Overrides — do not commit (added to .gitignore)

## Communication style
- Short, direct responses. No end-of-response summary.
- Do not rephrase my question before answering.
- Propose one solution, not a list of options unless explicitly asked.

## Personal workflow
- Always read the full file before modifying it.
- Always verify compilation (`mvn verify` or `npm run typecheck`) before declaring a task done.
- When intent is unclear, ask ONE targeted question.

## Local environment
- Backend on port 8080, frontend on port 5173.
- Active Spring profile in dev: `local` (file `application-local.yml` ignored by Git).
- Local database: `taskflow_dev` on PostgreSQL localhost:5432.
- No Docker in daily dev — PostgreSQL and Redis run natively.

## Code preferences
- Lombok allowed on the backend: `@Data`, `@Builder`, `@RequiredArgsConstructor`.
- No JavaDoc except on public service interfaces.
- Prefer Java records for immutable DTOs.
- On the frontend, prefer arrow functions over function declarations.

## Work in progress
- Testing Testcontainers for repository integration tests.
- Exploring Spring AI for automatic task summary generation.
